headline: 9 Stocks to Buy Before Their Earnings Reports
summary: FEATURE  Finding stocks that can rise on the back of strong earnings is becoming difficult. Evercore strategists screened for the few that can.   Right now, stocks are so expensive it might be hard for them to rise much further—even in the case of better-than-expected earnings.

headline: 'Very troubling': AI's self-investment spree sets off bubble alarms on Wall Street
summary: The companies at the center of the artificial intelligence boom are increasingly investing billions of dollars in each other — and analysts say that the increasing entanglement is adding to risk of an AI bubble.
